snippet.title: Isolated Room -  Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
What to do when your days are not going well? What to do when you need to wake up and manage a troubled life, in which you need to work, eat well and still have time for yourself? Isolated Room is about that, and maybe a little more.

Stay tuned at http://www.blackhole.games

Available now on Steam: https://bit.ly/IsolatedRoomSteam
Follow us on Twitter: http://twitter.com/BlackHoleGames_
Follow us on Instagram: http://instagram.com/blackholegames
Also on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/BlackHoleGames
